<h1>吓</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#000099;">xià</span><span class=alesi>(xia4)</span> , <span style="color:#000099;">hè</span><span class=alesi>(he4)</span> , <span style="color:#000099;">hà</span><span class=alesi>(ha4)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 吓 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 吓</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/scare" style="color:black;">scare</a>, <a href="/dictionary/frighten" style="color:black;">frighten</a>; <a href="/dictionary/intimidate" style="color:black;">intimidate</a></p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 6<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 6 strokes: <a href="/character/在" title="zai4: be at, in, on; consist in, rest">在</a>, <a href="/character/有" title="you3: have, own, possess; exist">有</a>, <a href="/character/地" title="de: earth; soil, ground; region">地</a>, <a href="/character/会" title="hui4: assemble, meet together; meeting">会</a>, <a href="/character/而" title="er2: and; and then; and yet; but">而</a>, <a href="/character/那" title="na4: that, that one, those">那</a>, <a href="/character/自" title="zi4: self, private, personal; from">自</a>, <a href="/character/年" title="">年</a>, <a href="/character/过" title="guo4: pass, pass through, go across">过</a>, <a href="/character/后" title="hou4: queen, empress, sovereign; (simp. for 後) behind, rear, after">后</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/口" title="Kangxi radical 30">口</a>&nbsp;30.3</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 5 <br><small>Other HSK 5 characters: <a href="/character/恋" title="lian4: love; long for, yearn for; love">恋</a>, <a href="/character/辞" title="ci2: words, speech, expression, phrase">辞</a>, <a href="/character/眉" title="mei2: eyebrows; upper margin of book">眉</a>, <a href="/character/尺" title="">尺</a>, <a href="/character/腰" title="yao1: waist; kidney">腰</a>, <a href="/character/辈" title="bei4: generation, lifetime; class">辈</a>, <a href="/character/贴" title="tie1: paste to, stick on; attached to">贴</a>, <a href="/character/滑" title="hua2: slip, slide; slippery, polished">滑</a>, <a href="/character/赏" title="shang3: reward, grant, bestow; appreciate">赏</a>, <a href="/character/骂" title="ma4: accuse, blame, curse, scold">骂</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-5" title="List of HSK 5 characters" style="white-space: nowrap;">mor